(100a + 10c + b) + (100b + 10a + c) + (100b + 10c + a) + (100c + 10a + b) + (100c + 10b + a) = 3194
122a + 212b + 221c = 3194
122, 212, 221 \equiv 5 (mod\space9)
3194 \equiv 8 (mod\space9)
5(a + b + c) \equiv 8 (mod\space9)
a + b + c = 7
